modName: Race Menu Preset - Nord Beauty - Dusa
descriptionHtml:
An original preset by me, took countless hours to sculpt her out with Racemenu.

As I think I am ever closer to quitting Skyrim*, I decided to upload her preset before I quit, following my previous oblivion character.
http://www.nexusmods.com/oblivion/mods/41856/?

Dusa is slavic, roughly translating into "Soul" or "Spirit"

Permissions:
Feel free to upload her anywhere else, credit me as creator.
Feel free to convert her to a follower, credit me as co-creator/inspiration

[i]Please do not attempt to use this file for profit.[/i]

*OK, maybe never quitting, not until the next good-to-great TES game anyway.
